io.jeo.mongo

Class MongoFeature

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.jeo.mongo.MongoFeature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Feature

    public class MongoFeature
extends Object
implements Feature
    Feature wrapper around a mongo DBObject.

    This class uses a Mapping instance to map feature geometries and properties.

    Author:
    Justin Deoliveira, OpenGeo
